{"tid":1115173,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］麻煩大家用返正確既中文字","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T17:54:32.000Z","uid":224952,"like":64,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e761de6cb3b4a4a128471d690fdd0f087a3c8b4c","tid":1115173,"uid":224952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"自從主權移交之後，香港中文文化被嚴重侵蝕<br />\n依加周街都聽到人講手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早十幾廿年前邊撚到會聽到人講手機呢兩隻字<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">電話</span></span>先係正字，香港一向都叫開手提電話，廣告都成日聽到啦「駕駛時切勿使用手提電話」乜撚野手機，難聽到。<br />\n<br />\n仲有「優化」呢個字，即係點？<br />\n死人蝗語懶係溫柔懶係靚咁，屌，改善改進升級咁撚多字形容，係要用優化，有問題就要改善維修，唔係用優化懶係冇事咁，夠膽死連政府都用「優化」呢個詞語。<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲垃圾報紙佬，小三內地小車煙火屏幕背包失聯，屌你老尾學過中文未呀。<br />\n<br />\n唔該睇到呢個post既人麻煩用返正確既中文字，由手機呢個字做起，我真係唔忍心啲中文比人亂鳩咁用，以前港英年代啲鬼佬都唔會用亂用中文字啦「布政司」呢三個字係我聽過最優雅既職位，相反中共死都要套自己啲字落黎，邊個地方當香港係二等公民大家有眼睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82cb91f64bd55e5ce933c64ed14c65629774d82","tid":1115173,"uid":78683,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"吾系貢牙"},{"pid":"c1a64d6a72b356814585cd493ee9680cb21d2644","tid":1115173,"uid":38904,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"正確<span style=\"color: red;\">既</span>-&gt;嘅"},{"pid":"63bbd593d4115dd1e0953a4a9baecc5db5643b16","tid":1115173,"uid":59920,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"岩🦷😂"},{"pid":"52d6e52e0545b800c0f16556ce000b162b21ccf6","tid":1115173,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"應驗左當年條九七前後<br />\n只係唔係exactly由大哥大變高幹高咁解"},{"pid":"df71963a29a9ad0a662b53db3aa1f6c823aa825e","tid":1115173,"uid":224952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15f10694014ea12faa29d63b0fe4811e3007654","tid":1115173,"uid":224952,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648270f108a9c86985460ed6313ed14db59821ad","tid":1115173,"uid":90457,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人本身都係用「五毫子」<br />\n「五毛」係支國詞嚟，唔好再用，邊個再用就屌到佢上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a295fef3f0707936283fb156a82c9a3776ff97","tid":1115173,"uid":175598,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"071db5b69cda1389bdba747dd082c75e8c9c3a7a","tid":1115173,"uid":65401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"真係好撚難聽"},{"pid":"e907a0ed124460adb5e716676c7cfbc0aea7e0c2","tid":1115173,"uid":186125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"機電署個優化升降機計劃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227eeb5eb3baa3be83f2315b6cad2af3ac4dfed9","tid":1115173,"uid":151233,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"咁你會講「打電話」定「打手機」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cedf8b7e2e6b2181507a066b63f7786a5aeff8f","tid":1115173,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"講英文咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387b8e782e728de29b621f6efccda7317d0349cf","tid":1115173,"uid":44391,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"473f5ab515ce03d63a6af20ecb0fb76618fa70d1","tid":1115173,"uid":224952,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"227eeb5eb3baa3be83f2315b6cad2af3ac4dfed9","tid":1115173,"uid":1